title: Disney Q4 bolstered by strong results from streaming, 'Inside Out 2' and 'Deadpool & Wolverine' - Yahoo Finance

Operating income for the entertainment segment, which includes its movie studio and parts of its television wing, more than quadrupled to $1.07 billion.
